After the use of the support (2 years), the company Arch.Design is obliged to continue to operate the mini-garden for 3 more years at its own expense.
The preparation of this project took a whole year, with the company Economy Rating providing active assistance in the application process.
The children take care of fully qualified staff - a nurse and a kindergarten teacher, the kindergarten can visit children without age restrictions, although most of them are over three years old.
And since this is about a mini-kindergarten, only 5 children may be present at the same time, but the day is different over several children.
The kindergarten operation is flexible to the needs of the parents, the children of all employees have the same rights in terms of the use of the kindergarten - regardless of the company hierarchy and their respective position.
