Also for the price of an impairment of their privacy.
"We are trying to tell everyone that this is not about spying around, but about an effective means of reducing the likelihood of the tragedy," Petr Pilin of the company Macro Weil, one of the suppliers of GPS tracking devices on the Czech market.
